Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives - Season 21, Episode 4




Worldwide Flavorfest

This trip, Guy's getting a taste of global flavor. In Cincinnati, the Jamaican joint firing up their trademark jerk chicken and spicy snapper. In Boston, the lunch-only spot serving a full plate of authentic Italian, like porcini cascioni and rosettes. And in Duluth, the flavorful border dweller dishin' out a taste of Thailand with dishes like the Bangkok burrito and a killer lamb curry.




Original Air Date: 26-Sep-2014
